{noformat}
https://ajthedrummerboy.atlassian.net/browse/EPICC-28?utm_term=&utm_source=jira-slack&utm_medium=referral-external&atlOrigin=eyJpIjoiNjZkYjE0NTE0YzM1NDBlNDkyODdiN2MwZDk1ZDcyNmEiLCJwIjoiamlyYS1zbGFjay1pbnQifQ
{noformat}

Since none of the parameters are necessary for the issue load or redirection, do give customers the option to trim off the parameter or just remove it entirely since it serve no purpose from customer point of view and it also clogs up the browser history rendering it hard to browse through.
